author: sbailliez
msg: Fix from Ingmar Stein <stein@xtramind.com> for colorization.
Errors are now always red whereas warnings are purple. Errors have a
higher priority, i.e. if a package has test classes that produced errors
and warnings, it is colored red.
Added a fix for package name sorting (it was incorrectly sorted by class name)
Still need to clean up the html to use css like junit-noframes.xsl does.
